    "If students are generally positive about ChatGPT's use it is staff who express more concerns.",
    "Cardon et al. (2023) conducted a survey of business communication instructors.",
    "The main concern of this group of educators was that students would use it to cheat.",
    "But they saw a range of negative impacts on learning, such as They also acknowledged that it can be helpful e.g.",
    "in the early stages of writing, and certainly enhanced the efficiency of writing."
